{"tid":1631330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post，所有手足入嚟傾","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:41.000Z","uid":86495,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c299b054e1526bc9203415348ecd851f95a20427","tid":1631330,"uid":86495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"聽日一定要再遍地開多次花搞18區，但好多手足可能冇目標，而加就傾下大方向<br />\n<br />\n首要目標，搞黨鐵，聽日搞黨鐵係十分重要，因為可以令到好多香港市民星期二被罷工！大家要諗定方法開閘入去搞，最好搞哂每一個站，盡搞啦<br />\n<br />\n次要目標，搞親中議員辦事處，同埋幫美心，元氣，吉野家裝修。<br />\n<br />\n最後就係幫哂所有中資鋪頭整裝飾！<br />\n<br />\n大家要有個大方向一齊做，先可以團結！如果唔係個個話18區，但有冇人知18區出哂嚟要做啲咩？好多人都唔知㗎"},{"pid":"ed9ad820176aca55273665ef3e8459572eaa409a","tid":1631330,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"267ffbcacf63140854d10063a0f669b8fb14bacb","tid":1631330,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vgcHuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vgcHuT.jpg&h=6f7251cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f935f7bb2bcc9fe778c5e0053abb9a64722c0902","tid":1631330,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5cb0eaa255473ee8850d6b984542d82625858597","tid":1631330,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"982ecb740703a17b94c0cc47d91fdd8b5afe7909","tid":1631330,"uid":86495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推，要全部人都知開花係點開花"},{"pid":"1b2149bd64c23f8c